13. O-O-O c5! {[%cal Gb8c6,Rc8c1][%csl Rd4]} { After having castled long, White can't switch to slow positional play trying to utilize the bishop pair in some long ending; therefore, it makes sense to start our counterplay as soon as possible. } 
