17. Qc3 ( { After } 17.Nxf6+ Kf7 18.Qc3 Bg7! { , we pick up the knight on f6 due to the threat of discovered check on f3. } ) Bg7 { Simply completing our development. } 
18. O-O O-O {[%cal Gc7e7,Gf6f5,Gf5f4,Ye7g5]} 
19.-- ( { Intending ...Qe7 followed by ...f5, with excellent counterplay. Most probably, White should prevent it by playing } 19.Qb4 { , but then even insisting on the idea with } 19...h6!? { makes a lot of sense. In general, I believe in our chances, as I can't quite see what White is hoping for, whereas we have many long-term prospects. } )
