15. Bf1 f5! {[%csl Rd4,Re4]} { This is the point of @@StartFEN@@r4rk1/1p1q1ppp/2p1pnb1/p7/PbBP4/1QN1PP2/1P4PP/R1BR2K1 b - - 1 13@@EndFEN@@ 13...Nd5 - we are able to strike at White's center immediately, giving us plenty of counterplay. It all feels a bit overextended for White, and I like our chances. } 
