11. Qb3 { Trying to bring the queen back to the defense is the best try. } Rb8 
12. Qd1 Nd3+ { There are many other tempting moves, but this is the most straightforward. } 
13. Bxd3 Bxd3 {[%cal Re1g1][%csl Gd3]} { With our strong bishop on d3, White will never really be able to castle short, giving us fantastic compensation. Even if White one day in the future managed to castle, we would still have excellent compensation in the style of the Meran Attempt chapter. [/course/140404/7] } 
