8. Nxc4 { I imagine almost everyone would play this as White. } Bd5 {[%cal Ge7e5,Gb7b5]} 
9. e4 { Nothing else really makes any sense. } b5 { Very strong and rather difficult to spot in advance. We take the knight with our b-pawn instead, which greatly improves our structure. } 
