13. Nc3 e5! { Following the old rule that flank attacks should be met by a central strike! } 
14. dxe5 Rd8 {[%cal Gd7e5,Ge5d3,Ge8g8][%csl Re1]} { We will regain the e5-pawn next, and for the remaining pawn, we have a fantastic piece play in the center. Our king will be completely safe on g8, whereas White's king will be eternally weak. } 
