19. Bc2 {[%mdl 32768]} { A typical position from the ...exf5-structure. With their last move, White has a very concrete idea in mind. What should we do about it? } Nef6! {[%cal Rf2f3][%csl Re3]} { White's idea is to push f3 and e4. Therefore, we prophylactically retreat the knight so that the e3-pawn will be hanging. Now White lacks a good plan. } ( { Instead, } 19...Re7 20.f3 Nef6 21.e4 { would become very messy. } ) 
